Extract time-level information

timedata.Rd

Extract time-level information

timedata(x)

Arguments

x

A list containing element xyz

Value

A tibble with time-level data

Examples

fn <- system.file("extdata/bds_v3.0/smocc/Laura_S.json",
  package = "jamesdemodata")
timedata(read_bds(fn))
